---
description: After editing Go sources in this project, always build the Linux binary.
globs: ["**/*.go"]
---

When you modify any `.go` file in this project, run the Linux build so the binary is updated:

- On Windows (PowerShell): `.\build-linux.ps1`
- Or: `make build-linux` (if make is available)

Output binary: `bin/netgate` (for Ubuntu/Linux).
